{"tid":1666253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動］港島手足今晚萬一去唔到元朗，可以咁做：","createTime":"2019-10-21T02:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T07:43:08.000Z","uid":322373,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b68b3af43afcf9ff25282191eb6aec80c6cdc222","tid":1666253,"uid":322373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:06:36.000Z","msg":"灣仔銅鑼灣，以至港島距離元朗好遠，搭巴士去到，夜晚都未必走到。如果去到就去，元朗今晚係主角！<br />\n<br />\n我提議響應（見下面連結），<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">去唔到元朗嘅港島人，7:00集中喺銅鑼灣車站大堂和平靜坐！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n盡量集中銅鑼灣！<strong>萬一滿座，可以考慮改到灣仔或金鐘站，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自行決定</span></span></strong>。</strong>手足唔方便去，可以留守自己就近車站，但盡量先去銅鑼灣。<br />\n<br />\n元朗721恐襲政府一直未有起訴任何人，亦未有狗負上失職責任，今晚遍地開花，係要提醒香港人：721，唔見人！<br />\n<br />\n#1021<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳送門：<br />\n<br />\n不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"74ab9a8ef04e18bd20768ad8cbb1dee33ae6dbe7","tid":1666253,"uid":164008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:08:51.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n討論清真寺<br />\n勿忘721"},{"pid":"8853637b92a630ceb593e0ea94b369fabc4ebd36","tid":1666253,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:09:08.000Z","msg":"遍地開花"},{"pid":"d7e45838c02718eb7b2c0288873b92bf371bfd64","tid":1666253,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:09:54.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n［第十期牆紙］訴求在沉默中進化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1662489/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1662489/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERdqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=fd1f2aa7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperE